{"tid":1161144,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Suunto 潛水電腦 Sensor問題","createTime":"2019-05-19T03:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T06:43:52.000Z","uid":78413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6592baa5f8b8dec95b4a638482bcf124f3a82fe1","tid":1161144,"uid":78413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:22:26.000Z","msg":"我上年9月喺Diving Express (DE) 買左隻潛水電腦 (Suunto Eon Core)，用左十幾潛。上年十月到而家，大約半年無潛過水，一直擺會喺個櫃入面。琴日充完電佢就一直喺Dive Mode入面，明明喺陸地，但佢個sensor話我喺3.2m水深。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCN3BfP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCN3BfP.jpg&h=5291c5be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住我擺左佢一晚，睇下佢會唔會好返。佢頭先啱啱用哂嘅電，點知就出左以下嘅Error畫面：<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aQMy2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aQMy2v.jpg&h=0f69249b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我又接駁返電源，點知佢又入返Dive Mode，出唔返正常Mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎去維修大概要幾多日？同埋應該拎返去DE定係Suunto維修中心會快啲？有無人試過同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baacdf0fdf61b8b8e4d0f284731529438111bee6","tid":1161144,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27601d488c63b99cad65e4adad4e0e0fb0845af5","tid":1161144,"uid":78413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baacdf0fdf61b8b8e4d0f284731529438111bee6","tid":1161144,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"Haha, 主要係俾潛水(Scuba Diving)用，但都有啲係專for freedive"},{"pid":"b3d32a77b7beaeb7c4c17272ac486e2f820c3c2a","tid":1161144,"uid":40609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:33:20.000Z","msg":"Suunto 通病黎<br />\n成日鬼潛"},{"pid":"15ba3a05276360bdff95e655ff86622d9f75be9a","tid":1161144,"uid":247836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20